    "intro": "Interpretation moves from what the text says to what it means — probing the author's intent within the canonical framework of the Abrahamic covenant and tracing how Genesis 35's theology develops across the canon. The movements below follow the chapter's argument structure, not its verse sequence, grouping pericopes by theological function.",
